{"type": "article", "id": 23547, "title": "加拿大湖里这些美丽的冰冻气泡，是沼气的杰作", "description": "每年冬天，你都能在发生同样自然现象的湖上看到这样的美景", "date": "2016-03-09T19:00:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 24634, "name": "沼气"}, {"id": 24635, "name": "湖"}, {"id": 6132, "name": "加拿大"}], "category": 5, "author": 18, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 152, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122050dXJlxD8QYLCgrZFm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">加拿大阿尔伯塔（Alberta）省的亚伯拉罕（Abraham）湖是一座人工湖，这个人工湖每年冬天都会出现一种奇观——湖面下聚集着大量的冰冻气泡。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071220460eGRDQ25zHJmTKsX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.44907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122046Sv3LUMaNQxB41XH0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122047nkt63xFDCAs5R4E8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071220470fwYh3nE59mGBdPQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122048Iqzk8nDFsBKdmY6C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122049MiKqL0mve7CQ41zT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">之所以会出现这种现象，是亚伯拉罕湖湖床植物释放的沼气和湖面低温所致。沼气不停地涌向湖面，当气温降到一定程度时，湖面开始结冰，并将这些气泡形成的空腔一起保留下来，随着气温降低，这些冰冻气泡就会不断地堆积起来，最后变成我们现在看到的样子。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">根据阿拉斯加大学费尔班克斯分校（The University of Alaska Fairbanks）的科学家 Katey M. Walter Anthony <a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/08/science/methane-has-never-looked-so-beautiful.html\">所言</a>，这样的景色在世界上许多发生同样自然现象的天然湖和人工湖都能看到。</p>\n<p class=\"\">卡尔加里大学（University of Calgary）的博士在读生 Ross 则提醒慕名而来的游客注意安全小心跌落。当她在拍摄下面这张照片时，为防止大风将自己吹走而在鞋底安上了鞋钉。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122050gwuOzk8jPrhZKpJQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}